  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Important announcement by Jaffna Municipal Council to the public",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the fuel crisis, the Jaffna Municipal Council's solid waste disposal operation has become critical and the Jaffna Municipal Council Health Committee Chairman V. Partheepan has issued an urgent request to the people.",
        "The current economic crisis in the country has affected the activities of the Jaffna Municipal Council to the extent that it affects the people.",
        "Thus the solid waste disposal process being carried out by the Jaffna Municipal Council has become a very challenging one.",
        "In June 2021 a new solid waste disposal mechanism was developed. Although all 27 districts, including the present Jaffna Municipal Council, have been provided with one tractor and disposed of, only 9 tractors are currently engaged in solid waste disposal due to the ongoing fuel crisis.",
        "This has led to the emergencies of waste management. New schedules have been prepared in response to the mayor's request to visit a home at least once a week. People have to put up with the crisis in solid waste disposal caused by the fuel crisis.",
        "We have declared 9 places under the Jaffna Municipal Council where people can sort their waste and hand it over when waste cannot be disposed of. Somehow they can give the waste in the allotted places near them.",
        "We will make this public in the press in a few days. Arrangements will be made for the event to take place from 6 a.m. to 6 p.m.",
        "So people should give full cooperation for this emergency sanitation management. Also minimize waste as much as possible.",
        "Also, if our employees pressurize us by saying, \"We will spend money only if you give us money\", if we report it to the Jaffna Municipal Council, appropriate action will be taken.",
        "The public can contact 0716390000 to lodge complaints."
      ],
